          <li>An accreditation certificate.</li>
          <li>A tree planted in your name.</li>
          <li>Automatic entry to the International CSR Excellence Awards.</li>
          <li>Entry in our CSR accredited members directory.</li>
          <li>An Annual CSR Health Check – One-hour free consultation meeting.</li>
            <li>CSR accreditation consultation call 6 months before your accreditation renewal.</li>
            <li>Exclusive members discounts for training, webinars and events.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
